---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Arhum Savera — open to backend, AI systems, and senior engineering roles.">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Get in Touch</h1>
    <p>
      Open to senior engineering roles, technical collaborations, and
      conversations about backend architecture and production AI systems.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="contact-grid">

      <div class="panel contact-main">
        <h2>Let&rsquo;s talk</h2>
        <p>
          Email is the best way to reach me. I read everything and respond
          to messages that include enough context to have a real conversation.
        </p>
        <a class="contact-email" href="mailto:arhum.a.savera@gmail.com">
          arhum.a.savera@gmail.com
        </a>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arhumsavera/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link-btn">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/arhumsavera" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link-btn">
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="/resume.pdf" download="Arhum_Savera_Resume.pdf" class="contact-link-btn">
            Resume
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel contact-detail">
        <h2>What I&rsquo;m open to</h2>
        <ul class="open-to-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ot-label">Senior IC roles</span>
            Backend, AI/ML platform, or full-stack with a strong systems focus.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ot-label">AI platform work</span>
            LLM orchestration, agent tooling, retrieval systems, production ML.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ot-label">Technical collaboration</span>
            Open-source, side projects, or consulting on backend and AI architecture.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ot-label">Talks & writing</span>
            Happy to discuss agent engineering, voice workflows, or production AI patterns.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Good messages to send</h2>
      <p class="hint-intro">
        I respond faster when the message has enough context to skip a round-trip.
        Anything like:
      </p>
      <ul class="hint-list">
        <li>What the team or company does and what the role looks like technically.</li>
        <li>Why you think there&rsquo;s a fit — specific is better than generic.</li>
        <li>Preferred timeline and next step (call, async, etc.).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:inline>
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-main h2,
  .contact-detail h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .contact-main p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
  }

  .contact-email {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #7dd3fc;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }
  .contact-email:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: #bae6fd; }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-link-btn {
    border: 1px solid #2a4060;
    background: #0e1e30;
    color: #9ec4e8;
    padding: 0.38rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 130ms ease, color 130ms ease;
  }
  .contact-link-btn:hover { border-color: #4b7aab; color: #cce2ff; }

  .open-to-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .open-to-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ot-label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .hint-intro {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  .hint-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .hint-list li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
